<template>
  <a-result
    status="success"
    title="成功发起投票项目"
    sub-title="请注意保存投票项目返回ID:{{ID}}"
  >
    <template #extra>
      <a-button key="console" type="primary" @click="finish">完成</a-button>
      <a-button key="buy" @click="voting">投票</a-button>
    </template>
  </a-result>
</template>

<script>
import emitter from '@/utils/bus';
import { defineComponent} from 'vue';
export default defineComponent({

 data () {
    return {
      ID:''
    }
  },
  created(){
    emitter.on("ResID",msg=>{
      this.ID = msg.ID
    });
  },

  methods:{
  finish(){
      this.$emit('finish')
    },
    voting(){
      this.$router.push('/voting')
    }
    }
  

});

</script>
